---
---
<section id="about" class="py-28 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

    <div>
      <p class="section-label mb-4">About the Studio</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-300 leading-tight mb-6">
        CHAHONG ROOM<br/>
        <em class="text-gold">Hair Studio</em>
      </h2>
      <span class="gold-line gold-line-left"></span>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5 font-300 text-sm">
        CHAHONG ROOM is a flagship premium salon in Myeongdong, Seoul — part of Korea's renowned CHAHONG beauty brand founded by master stylist Cha Hong. Known for its refined boutique atmosphere, the studio blends trend-leading Korean design with a strong focus on natural beauty and balance.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8 font-300 text-sm">
        Our experienced directors and designers offer personalized consultations entirely in English — delivering exceptional results for international visitors in a calm, sophisticated environment. Whether you're looking for a subtle refresh or a complete K-beauty transformation, we bring skill, care, and creativity to every appointment.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2.5">
        {['English Friendly', 'Foreigner Specialist', 'Premium K-Beauty', 'Scalp Experts', 'Korean Trends'].map(t => (
          <span class="px-3.5 py-1.5 border border-dark-border text-[0.65rem] tracking-widest uppercase text-text-muted hover:border-gold hover:text-gold transition-all cursor-default">{t}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/about-us" class="btn-outline">Read Our Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      {[
        { icon: '✂️', title: 'Precision Cuts', desc: 'Korean wolf cuts, layered cuts, see-through bangs and trend styling for every face shape.' },
        { icon: '🎨', title: 'Expert Coloring', desc: 'Balayage, toning, bleaching and K-pop fashion colors crafted with precision.' },
        { icon: '💆', title: 'Head Spa', desc: 'Aromatherapy scalp massage and deep cleanse for ultimate relaxation and hair health.' },
        { icon: '🧪', title: 'Korean Perm', desc: 'C-curl, S-curl, digital and setting perms for transformative texture results.' },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="bg-dark-card border border-dark-border p-6 hover:border-gold transition-colors duration-300 group">
          <span class="text-2xl mb-3 block">{item.icon}</span>
          <h3 class="font-display text-sm font-600 mb-2 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-xs leading-relaxed font-300">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
